PrecisAmendment to the MARITIME PROVINCES FISHERY REGULATIONS which corrects an anomaly in the wording of section 71 so that authorized professional guides will not be required to use their own personal tags on salmon that are hooked by a physically challenged or inexperienced client and then landed with the guides' assistance.
